1. *Zakona* je obavezno da poštujemo. (It is obligatory to respect the law.) 
2. Oni se pridržavaju *zakona*. (They abide by the law.)
3. Ugovor je u skladu sa *zakonom*. (The contract is in accordance with the law.)
4. *Zakon* je zaštitio njihova prava. (The law protected their rights.)
5. Oni se pridržavaju *zakonodavstva*. (They abide by the legislation.)
6. Svi smo podložni *zakonima*. (We are all subject to the laws.)